## The Sliding Window Template

Useful for solving substrings or subsegments with maximum lengths or coordinate checks inside O(N) speed limits.

```java
int left = 0;
int right = 0;
Map<Character, Integer> counts = new HashMap<>();
int maxLength = 0;

while (right < array.length) {
    char c = array[right];
    counts.put(c, counts.getOrDefault(c, 0) + 1);

    while (counts.get(c) > limit) { // Shrink barrier
        char l = array[left];
        counts.put(l, counts.get(l) - 1);
        left++;
    }

    maxLength = Math.max(maxLength, right - left + 1);
    right++;
}
```
